spirit:component.spirit:name: basic_dmt_c_counter_binary_v12_0_0
spirit:component.spirit:description: The Xilinx LogiCORE Binary Counter creates up counters, down counters, and up/down counters with output widths ranging up to 256 bits. The upper count limit is user programmable, and the counter's increment value can either be user-defined, or specified via an external input port.
